OL,3,CLaw against sexually abusing bodies to
OL,4,Cbe strengthened by Government
OL,6,FCriminals who sexually abuse dead
OL,7,Fpeople will face tougher sentences
OL,8,Funder Government-backed reforms
OL,9,Fdeveloped in the wake of necrophiliac
OL,10,Fkiller David Fuller's mortuary abuse.
OL,12,FJustice minister Laura Farris said the
OL,13,FGovernment will amend existing 2003
OL,14,Flegislation to increase the maximum
OL,15,Fprison sentence for the sexual
OL,16,Fpenetration of a body from two years
OL,17,Fto seven years.
