OL,6,FMPs heard the changes will also create
OL,7,Fa new offence of "sexual activity with
OL,8,Fa corpse" with a maximum prison
OL,9,Fsentence of five years to cover non-
OL,10,Fpenetrative offences.
OL,12,FThe Government will implement the
OL,13,Fchange by supporting a Criminal
OL,14,FJustice Bill amendment initially
OL,15,Fbrought forward by Conservative former
OL,16,Fministers Greg Clark and Dame Tracey
OL,17,FCrouch.
