OL,6,FMr Clark, speaking during report stage
OL,7,Fof the Bill, told the Commons: "All of
OL,8,FFuller's crimes are, frankly,
OL,9,Funspeakable, but as well as the
OL,10,Fcurrent sentencing limit being
OL,11,Fabsurdly inadequate to deal with, in
OL,12,Feffect, the rape of dead bodies, it
OL,13,Fdoes not cover at all any form of
OL,14,Fsexual assault that is non-
OL,15,Fpenetrative."
OL,17,FHe added there is "clearly a gap" in
OL,18,Fthe law which needs to be closed,
OL,19,Fadding: "That's what this new clause
OL,20,Faims to do."
