OL,6,FMs Farris earlier told the debate: "It
OL,7,Fis perhaps a rare thing in 2024 that
OL,8,Fan offence can be identified which
OL,9,FParliament has not even previously
OL,10,Fconsidered.
OL,12,F"But such was the extent of Fuller's
OL,13,Foffending, we've had to do so and the
OL,14,FGovernment is pleased to confirm the
OL,15,FSexual Offences Act 2003 will be
OL,16,Famended under this legislation to
OL,17,Fcapture the sexual touch of a corpse,
OL,18,Fwith a new maximum sentence of seven
OL,19,Fyears for penetrative offences, and
OL,20,Ffive for non-penetrative acts."
